<item>
            <title>[LU-4726] vfs_rename api change</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4726</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In newer kernel versions the kernel api vfs_rename() has been changed to take 5 arguments instead of 4.  This breaks the lustre build, even pure client-only builds.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I plan to push a wrapper for vfs_rename() with autoconf support to adapt to different numbers of arguments.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
